			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/CTY_Main_A\r\n- Use \"oe MT_Start\", enter the tombstone shop and go down into the Murder Tribunal\r\n- Ctrl+Shift+K the Death Knight guarding the door\r\n- Use \"oe MT_Dolor 1\" to get Dolor to appear at the door.\r\n- This AD will play once when you enter combat with him."
				},
